overview: Join Marty and Moog on an epic road trip across Japan in a car they've just bought off the internet. But before the trip kicks off, the boys have to decipher a cryptic note from the previous owner found on the steering wheel...  With stunning cinematography and epic cars, this 90 minute sequel to Turbos & Temples  delves into Japanese culture in a way that only Mighty Car Mods can.
title: TURBOS & TEMPLES 2
